ul.li:
Support for defining widget groups
          to be used with @EnabledWhen /
          @VisibleWhen annotations

A ClassCastException may occur when
          @DataProvider is used (Issue #
          93)

@EnabledWhen/@VisibleWhen do not work
          with not bound properties (Issue
          # 110)

@Action and @DataProvider in inherited
          methods are ignored (Issue
          # 115)
